Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:42.53,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(358,319,358,490)\fs17\1a&H45&}享尽季节美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:45.95,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(173,129,173,430)\1a&H45&\1c&H6365C9&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1}威\N尼\N斯\N火\N锅
