Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:45.95,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(284,19,284,210)\1a&H45&\1c&H6F8FC7&\3a&H6D&\3c&HF3FCF8&\bord1}水星维纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.95,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(246,0,246,130)\fs18\1a&H45&\4a&H2D&\4c&H0F0F0F&\shad1}临近海边  宁静的露天浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里还没去过天然的温泉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我只在电视节目里看过介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让身心都暖烘烘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在下次放假的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那蓝华也能去啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能去我也要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那就大家一起去温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去温泉要带什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈的话 不用你带也会一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾莉西亚前辈一起去温泉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人陷入妄想状态中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！赶紧结束练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟艾莉西亚前辈一起去温泉啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的工作结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝吗？虽然可能有点不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹的雪虫打扮得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要去体验第一次的温泉之旅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天要是水道的水也像温泉一样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯 烟囱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各家各户都开始用壁炉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的黄昏让人想家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总觉得是个温暖的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里也来织织看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能办得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 灯里的话一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力织出跟艾莉西亚前辈配对的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给亚利亚社长织一套围巾和帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 首先棒针要这么拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后像这样把毛线用食指勾住…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 结果都是让蓝华去预约的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我刚好知道一个很棒的温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经能看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,210)\fs34\frz6\c&HE0C8AA&\b1}土产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和期待的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们准备准备去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是灯里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把脱下来的衣服放在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我第一次跟不认识的人一起泡大浴池…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 蓝华 我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 等等我 等等我 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭笨手笨脚 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路很滑 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很特别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这里原来只是一个古旧的大宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有这座宅邸的是一对很有情调的老夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们发现温泉以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就把宅邸的一部分建成浴池了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建筑物本身虽然年久失修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也别有一番风味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像传说故事中的精灵之家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉还延伸到更深处…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉水好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡果然还是要喝咖啡牛奶啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很精通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是正确的喝法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通体舒畅啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 舒服地泡完澡之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是令人期待的晚餐时间～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝佳的美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有冻死人的特训 暖洋洋的又悠闲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前不再是大嗓门的前辈 而是艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极乐啊极乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 表情太陶醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级像换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？我这样很幸福 所以别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太舒服了 不小心就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是这种时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时的这时候 工作已经告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在准备晚餐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在这样的假日里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个单手套领航员才该拼命练习才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做了不该做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗？这么悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让你这么悠闲也是温泉的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了度过寒冷漫长的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是需要喘口气的时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 虽然我不习惯冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有可爱的雪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有令人想家的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有暖炉的话 好像也能变得喜欢冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还泡了温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉 一定是AQUA的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给我们的温暖的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再去泡一次温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人们说「温泉要泡三次」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有一个秘密场地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级心惊肉跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…还没到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 和大海连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 难道你来过这温泉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但是不好意思说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你太见外了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海和温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 灯里 没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 这么宽广却不游泳很浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然冬天的空气很清新 星星看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子汽水 是这里的名产哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像作梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱喝足了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟您一起的客人已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没赶上晚餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我请她们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛不太热烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要通宵好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从极乐…堕入了地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再…出一身汗…才去温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华接下来是艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和你决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我不想打了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们为了过冬 要回到水曲柳上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？要道别了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 AQUA的雪虫非常长寿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 到了明年的冬天一定还能见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新威尼斯有个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雪虫踏上旅程的时候就会下起初雪」的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪会那么冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 AQUA的冬天确实很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也有很多美好的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后每年都会期待着冬天的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雪虫也会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想来看看冬天的新威尼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总有一天会成为独当一面的领航员的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为一个独立的正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.35,0:24:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些 橘色的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:55.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風が凪いて 振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:02:04.44,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}夕映えに 照らされ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:14.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心までも 染まってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:25.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}見上げれば 響きだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:33.14,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}星たちの歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:43.29,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 遥か未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:52.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水面に 夢 広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:06.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 見つけよう まだ知らない 宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:13.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}あなたと一緒に 探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:55.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}轻风吹拂着 蓦然回首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:02:04.44,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在夕阳下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:14.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}让心中 染上温暖的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:25.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}抬头仰望 空中传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:33.14,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}是星星们的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:43.29,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}来 让我们出发 向着遥远的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:52.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}梦想 顺着水面 铺开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:06.86,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}快 让我们去寻找 那未被人知的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:13.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}跟你一起踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.41,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:56.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:23:00.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:12.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:19.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:28.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:31.46,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:39.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:45.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:53.58,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:24:00.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.41,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不变的景色 倒映在水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:56.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在缓缓流逝的时光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:23:00.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不断变化的季节中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}寻觅到 那不变的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:12.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}听 那幸福的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:19.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}像这样 一直 满溢于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:28.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的梦想 都将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:31.46,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 总会越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:39.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨后的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:45.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 总会展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:53.58,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的爱意 定会见到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:24:00.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常怀爱意 定能越过彩虹


